<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>The Catastrophic World Situation Demands Proletarian Revolution!</p>
<p>灾难性的世界形势要求无产阶级革命！</p>
<p>Unite Under the Red Banner of Maoism!</p>
<p>团结在毛主义的红旗下！</p>
<p>This May Day we address the international proletariat and the suppresed peoples and nations of the world reaffirming our solemn pledge to sweep away imperialism, revisionism and reaction off the face of the earth, with democratic, socialist and cultural revolutions, establishing and developing the dictatorship of the proletariat, through People’s War, until all humanity is liberated from all forms of oppression and exploitation, until we reach our unrenounceable final goal: Communism, the classless society where everyone’s needs will be satisfied, where there will be neither rich nor poor, exploiters and exploited, and where all will enjoy abundance. We will fight relentlessly and selflessly to create a new world, which will be totally and utterly opposite and different from this hell we live in now, a new society without the blood-sucking murderers who are the masters of the present.</p>
<p>这个五一劳动节，我们向国际无产阶级和世界上被压迫的人民和国家发表讲话，重申我们的庄严承诺，要用民主革命、社会主义革命和文化革命把帝国主义、修正主义和反动从地球上铲除，通过人民战争建立和发展无产阶级专政，直到全人类从一切形式的压迫和剥削中解放出来，直到我们达到我们不可放弃的最终目标：共产主义，一个每个人的需要都会得到满足的无阶级社会，一个没有富人和穷人的社会。我们将坚持不懈、无私地奋斗，以创造一个与我们现在所处的地狱截然相反、截然不同的新世界，一个没有作为当前的主宰的的吸血杀人犯的新社会。</p>
<p>The prevailing social order, the imperialist world system which develops amidst collusion and strife, and as part of it, US imperialism, the common enemy of the peoples of the whole world, is outdated and rotten to the core, it is sustained by the bloody bayonets of mercenary armies which will be powerless before us, the oppressed and exploited, when we organise our common power under the leadership of the proletarian vanguards, the Communist Parties, and rise up all over the world with arms in hand, destroying the old and building the new. Anyone who takes a look at the world today will see that we are facing a situation where the world proletarian revolution is the only way out, the only road for humanity and that the development of the objective and subjective conditions in the world are favourable for revolution; in this situation, it is up to us to break through with new People’s Wars into the new period of revolutions that the world has entered.</p>
<p>现在盛行的社会秩序，是在勾结和斗争中发展起来的帝国主义世界体系，全世界人民的共同敌人美帝国主义作为它的一部分，美帝国主义已经过时了，腐烂到了核心，它是由雇佣兵的血腥刺刀维持的，当我们在无产阶级的先锋队——共产党的领导下组织我们的共同力量，让全世界用手中的武器起义，破旧立新时，雇佣兵的血腥刺刀在被剥削和被压迫的我们面前是无能为力的。任何一个看当今世界的人都会看到，我们面临的形势是，世界无产阶级革命是人类的唯一出路、唯一道路，世界主客观条件的发展有利于革命，在这种情况下，我们要用新的人民战争来突破，进入世界已经到来的新的革命时期。</p>
</div>
